<h3 id="_4-核心机制三-交配选择-mating-selection" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_4-核心机制三-交配选择-mating-selection"><span>4. 核心机制三：交配选择（Mating Selection）</span></a></h3>
<ul>
<li>使用基于综合适应度 <span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>F</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>i</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">F(i)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.13889em;">F</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal">i</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span> 的 <strong>二元锦标赛选择</strong>；</li>
<li>当个体 <span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>F</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>i</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">F(i)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.13889em;">F</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal">i</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span> 相近时，可用距离或随机策略打破平局；</li>
<li>保证既有收敛压力，又不丧失种群多样性。</li>
